{"tid":832782,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"無線充電統計","createTime":"2018-09-23T04:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T16:02:52.000Z","uid":48917,"like":6,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ef6713524ff961b49ac41504d3a5581af93baa","tid":832782,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:47:35.000Z","msg":"依家無線充電都仲係好少人討論<br />\n巴絲有冇人用緊無線充電？<br />\n未發展成熟定太貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工同身邊冇人用<br />\n想買個 但大眾好似對無線好似冇咩睇法或追求<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾多人用緊無線充電 同有咩評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"573d1d60b24ba06c0c12c7b10b45a1740f5d33b8","tid":832782,"uid":15835,"like":64,"dislike":5,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"插住條線 瞓喺床玩 仲方便"},{"pid":"d04e2b20347b8e5e27b3e8befac9541b791845f5","tid":832782,"uid":30351,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:50:44.000Z","msg":"買左返屋企用，其實好唔方便。插線可以拎住玩，無線就唔得。最後拎左返公司，唔係位時就咁放係度叉，就ok方便。"},{"pid":"24e4c73d49c7a9994ccab8d384fa1e6327d12d85","tid":832782,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"573d1d60b24ba06c0c12c7b10b45a1740f5d33b8","tid":832782,"uid":15835,"like":64,"dislike":5,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"插住條線 瞓喺床玩 仲方便"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"我都覺<br />\n無線放係office 好用d？<br />\n隨時走得開<br />\n前幾年仲係賣點 <br />\n有幾多人真係會買個座<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20596afd0a04e89c96ae4fd47d63f75512a6617","tid":832782,"uid":126649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"充得慢 又熱"},{"pid":"b94abe87d978fd5134cb477ea6592e4a7675c4ef","tid":832782,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"喺log on買左個平野操用，點知慢到pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f0a9102a323